| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-3170 — Recovery Inhibition (interlock)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 4fa78a2e-861b-5ace-ac66-02ca4ad1ec67"
